275
00:18:03,607 --> 00:18:04,968
A cat...

276
00:18:04,968 --> 00:18:06,568
Excuse me?

277
00:18:06,568 --> 00:18:07,885
It's nothing.

278
00:18:07,885 --> 00:18:11,328
