279
00:18:11,328 --> 00:18:13,526
Our manufacturing process uses new technology

280
00:18:13,526 --> 00:18:16,307
that's carbon-free and environmentally-friendly.

281
00:18:16,307 --> 00:18:18,131
I see.

282
00:18:18,131 --> 00:18:22,168
From today onwards, we will be conducting lessons in here.

283
00:18:22,168 --> 00:18:25,538
I am Sawada Kyoka.
