284
00:18:25,538 --> 00:18:27,440
Since we're doing office yoga,
<i>[Sorry, my day has been chaotic, but I'll survive somehow...]</i>

285
00:18:27,440 --> 00:18:28,876
we'll focus on doing poses
<i>[Sorry, my day has been chaotic, but I'll survive somehow...]</i>

286
00:18:28,876 --> 00:18:33,049
that can help reduce shoulder stiffness and back pain
<i>[Sorry, my day has been chaotic, but I'll survive somehow...]</i>

